name: Gelato Sundae
description: Gelato Sundae is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Gelato and Sundae Driver. This strain is a flower product from Elev8 Seeds, a brand that offers high-quality cannabis seeds with various effects and flavors. Gelato Sundae is 20% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Gelato Sundae effects include relaxed, euphoric, and hungry. Medical marijuana patients often choose Gelato Sundae when dealing with symptoms associated with stress, pain, and appetite loss. Bred by Elev8 Seeds, Gelato Sundae features flavors like sweet, vanilla, and mint. The dominant terpene of this strain is caryophyllene. Gelato Sundae is a creamy and delicious hybrid that combines the fruity and creamy aromas of its parent strains.
